text: It's crazy and wild to recount the depth and breadth of the experiences we've shared together, right from the first sem. Too much things in common. Idk maybe apan saath mei productive nahi ho paaye ho itna lol itne lekin ik we've overcompensated that in the other spheres. From Dank edgy shit, pseudo-intellectual discussions aur FMC room se hall 3 Ek doosre ke friend/senior circle mei crashing we've done it all . Tere room ko kabhi apne room se kam nahi samjha . Passive-aggressive phases bhi apne badhiya chale hai but maybe its just coz in the end we both can't fake humble just coz others ... is insecure. We've been quite fucking blunt and honest with each other at times,about just about everything. I hope you already know without you, my college life would've lost most of its spice and shell-breaking experiences. Baaki no formalities.. aise hi naye stuff see introduction karate rahio aage bhi. Milte hai fir Delhi,Vadodara, Goa ,US .. Fuck it.. Kahi Bhi! <3 , Taxi!ðŸš•
